"""Test wait_for_job_complete timeout."""
self.common.retries = 0
rc, result, status, _ = self.common.wait_for_job_complete(self.data.job_list[1]
    )
self.assertEqual('RUNNING', status)
self.assertEqual(-1, rc)
self.assertIsNone(result)
mock.patch.object(common.CommonFunctions, '_is_job_finished', return_value=
    (False, '', 0, 'RUNNING', ''))
